  StyleBox["c", "TI"]], "InlineFormula",ExpressionUUID->
  "53493e3d-4114-a24c-8777-9d4bf0cca8c3"],
 " can be numeric or symbolic. The second argument can be a tensor train or a \
raw core list."
}], "Notes",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.993369624132288*^9, 3.99336962476186*^9}, 
   3.9933701307002773`*^9},
